data.description: Move-in ready Glendale condo! The lower level of this 2 bed, 2.5 bath condo features classic wood-look tile flooring, a beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances, cherry wood cabinetry, & plenty of counterspace. Enjoy one of this condo's 2 outdoor spaces on your extended, covered patio with added storage. Upstairs you'll find TWO spacious primary suites with soaring ceilings, ensuite bathrooms, & a balcony overlooking the small duck ponds on the property. This condo also comes with a rare 2-car garage for vehicles or additional storage. Monthly HOA fee covers water, sewer, & trash. Assumable VA loan! Maryland Lakes is a quiet community with 2 community pools, and quick access to Route 60 & 17, excellent schools, shopping, and dining - the options are endless!
